metadata.name: Land #1
metadata.description: S1 Genesis: 11.520 Lands with water filler spread over 80 sectors. The closer the Lands are to the Sector Center, the rarer they are: zone 1 is the closest, 5 is the farthest. Each Land has 25 building plots for a unique matrix of terrain and filler. 50% of Lands located in Zones from 1 to 5 have a Miner - to be revealed at public sale. Miners generate COINS periodically and let Land Owners earn up to 1.000 USD per year, depending on several factors. The Nemesis Lands total supply: 200.000, 10 Seasons, 10 Planets.
